Frost Blade

The druid may temporarily enchant a weapon with the
power of elemental ice, causing frost to coat its
striking surface.  This causes the weapon to deliver
additional damage.  It does not grant the bonus to
hit that Flame Blade does; however, the damage is
greater.

Command: frostblade <weapon>
Base Cost: 60 SP
Base Recovery: long
Base Effect: enhance (moderate)
Base Duration: long
Guild Level: 8
